name: Please Stand By -I Got Something To Say 102
description: Please Stand By utilizes the iconic SMPTE color bars template and changes the palette to bring into question viewers perceptions surrounding "standards of color." An offshoot of my original series, I Got Something To Say, adds an additional more literal message. Please Stand By, The Power Of Grayskull. Celebrating the resurrection of one of my favorite pop culture childhood icons, He-man, and the release of Revelations, a continuation of the original Masters of the Universe. I HAVE THE POWER!!!!
